 What is Docker Compose?

Docker Compose is used to define and run
multiple Docker containers using a single
docker-compose.yml file.



-------------------

docker compose up -d               # Start application
docker compose ps                  # Check running containers
docker compose logs                # View logs
docker compose exec web bash       # Access container
docker compose restart             # Restart services
docker compose stop                # Stop services
docker compose down                # Remove containers
docker compose build               # Build images
docker compose pull                # Pull images
docker compose logs                # Show logs
docker compose logs -f             # Follow logs
docker compose kill                # Force stop containers
docker compose rm                  # Remove stopped containers
docker compose down --volumes      # Remove containers and volumes
docker compose up --scale web=3    # Scale service